---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="About | AGNOSTO">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
    <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-cyber text-cyber-blue mb-6 sm:mb-8 text-center">ABOUT</h1>
    
    <div class="glass-card p-5 sm:p-8 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-cyber text-cyber-pink mb-3 sm:mb-4">Who is AGNOSTO?</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">
        AGNOSTO is a developer focused on creating specialized tools for content archiving and media playback.
        With a passion for cyberpunk aesthetics and efficient software design, AGNOSTO builds applications
        that are both functional and visually appealing.
      </p>
      <p class="text-sm sm:text-base">
        The name "AGNOSTO" derives from "agnostic" - representing the platform-agnostic approach to software
        development, ensuring tools work across different operating systems and environments.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="glass-card p-5 sm:p-8">
      <h2 class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-cyber text-cyber-pink mb-3 sm:mb-4">Projects & Philosophy</h2>
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">
        The projects developed under the AGNOSTO name focus on providing users with control over their digital content.
        The Fansly Scraper and Archive Player are designed to work together as a comprehensive solution for content
        creators and consumers.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-4 text-sm sm:text-base">
        All projects are open-source and available on GitHub, embracing the philosophy that software should be
        accessible, modifiable, and community-driven.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-4 sm:mt-6 flex justify-center sm:justify-start">
        <a 
          href="https://github.com/agnosto"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="px-4 sm:px-6 py-2 sm:py-3 bg-cyber-purple text-white font-cyber rounded inline-block hover:bg-cyber-pink transition-colors text-sm sm:text-base"
        >
          Visit GitHub Profile
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  .glass-card {
    background-color: rgba(13, 18, 30, 0.7);
    border: 1px solid rgba(5, 217, 232, 0.2);
    border-radius: 0.5rem;
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  }
  
  /* Mobile optimizations */
  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .glass-card {
      border-radius: 0.375rem;
    }
  }
</style>

